column5: Just noticed that my age has updated itself/was updated by someone else in my profile....and i thought i'd live forever!
I plan to live for ever. So far so good!
A couple more weeks and my age updates itself to 19  oh boy
I want to swear at you, but I am not allowed to. Besides, green is not my colour. Guess you can sit at the grown-up table at Lakair now.
one of these times  I will make it up there
19 or 91.....we all gotta go sometime. Just hopefully later than sooner.   I still need a good feed of perch....
